# Attention

CrossOver v2.7.4 was pushed out with a bug in the auto-update mechanism. You may have received an error for "setBadge".

Regardless, you will need to manually update to version 3.0.0 or above to continue getting fixes and updates to the app.
I'm really sorry about this, won't happen again!

[Download the newest version here](https://github.com/lacymorrow/crossover/releases/latest)

